Welcome to your new home! This charming 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom basement apartment is located in one of Brigham City’s most beautiful and quiet neighborhoods, offering both comfort and convenience.

Enjoy a full kitchen with plenty of cabinet space, a dedicated dining room, and your own in-unit washer and dryer for ultimate ease. Each bedroom is generously sized with ample closet space, and both bathrooms are clean, modern, and private—perfect for roommates or small families.

This cozy apartment is nestled in a peaceful residential area with tree-lined streets, nearby parks, and easy access to shopping, schools, and I-15.
